    ns2:light-04.entity-lit <http://www.ontologydesignpatterns.org/ont/fred/domain.owl#stand_1> .

<http://www.ontologydesignpatterns.org/ont/fred/domain.owl#disjunct_2> a <http://www.ontologydesignpatterns.org/ont/boxer/boxing.owl#Disjunct> ;
