<http://www.ontologydesignpatterns.org/ont/fred/domain.owl#neuter_1> a <http://www.ontologydesignpatterns.org/ont/fred/domain.owl#Moment>,
        <http://www.ontologydesignpatterns.org/ont/fred/domain.owl#Neuter>,
        owl:Thing .

<http://www.ontologydesignpatterns.org/ont/fred/domain.owl#serious_1> a <https://w3id.org/framester/data/propbank-3.4.0/RoleSet/serious-02> ;
    ns1:precedes <http://www.ontologydesignpatterns.org/ont/fred/domain.owl#have_1> ;
