    rdfs:subClassOf <http://www.ontologydesignpatterns.org/ont/fred/domain.owl#Face> .

<http://www.ontologydesignpatterns.org/ont/fred/domain.owl#Neuter> a owl:Thing .

<http://www.ontologydesignpatterns.org/ont/fred/domain.owl#atmosphere_1> a <http://www.ontologydesignpatterns.org/ont/fred/domain.owl#Atmosphere> .

