    ns2:have-03.possession <http://www.ontologydesignpatterns.org/ont/fred/domain.owl#expression_1> .

<http://www.ontologydesignpatterns.org/ont/fred/domain.owl#monster_1> a <http://www.ontologydesignpatterns.org/ont/fred/domain.owl#Monster> .

<http://www.ontologydesignpatterns.org/ont/fred/domain.owl#ominous_1> a <http://www.ontologydesignpatterns.org/ont/fred/domain.owl#Ominous> .

